EventVenue: College of Engineering, Bharati Vidyapeeth Pune
EventDescription: The Flutter Team is holding a global party for Flutter, and we’d love you to be part of the celebration! On December 13th, we’re hosting a Flutter Interact Viewing Party where we’ll share a variety of news and updates about Flutter. Be a part of celebration with our community, celebrate Flutter and inspire fellow community members. Share the posters on Facebook, Instagram and Twitter by using #dscbvppune #flutterinteract #flutterinteractdscbvppune to attend an amazing day to celebrate Flutter
content: On December 11th, interact, innovate and collaborate with the global community. Streaming live around the globe. If you want to join in, fill up the RSVP Form.
